description: Welcome to a radiant penthouse curated for elevated city living. This luxurious top floor 2 bed, 2 bath home with a private roof deck and garage parking crowns a boutique 2016 building with high-end upgrades throughout. A chef’s kitchen boasts Jenn-Air appliances, wine fridge, prep counter, and custom pantry. The sunlit living room flows to a private deck, anchored by a marble gas fireplace. Retreat to a serene primary suite with a spa-like marble bath and heated floors. The second bedroom and the guest bath are beautifully appointed. The crown jewel: a private roof deck with water, gas, and electric—perfect for entertaining against skyline views. Extras include central AC, in-unit laundry, hardwood floors, built-in audio, and private storage. This is more than a condo—it’s luxury living, redefined.
